com.googlecode.jsendnsca
Class NagiosSettingsFactory

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.jsendnsca.NagiosSettingsFactory

public class NagiosSettingsFactory
extends Object

Factory for creating NagiosSettings from a Properties object via file, stream or an instance. The names of the keys are documented in the NagiosSettingsFactory.PropertyKey enum. An example is shown below. You only need to provide keys for settings which you wish to override the default value of. See NagiosSettings for default values. 

 nagios.nsca.host=foobar
 nagios.nsca.port=7665
 nagios.nsca.password=password
 nagios.nsca.timeout=20000
 nagios.nsca.connect.timeout=10000
 nagios.nsca.encryption=xor

Since:
2.0.0
Author:
Raj Patel
